## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0879c-229">시간 UTC 기본값으로 설정 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0879c-229">The time will default to UTC.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0879c-230">현지 시간에서 시간을 지정 하려는 경우를 지정 합니다는 <xref:System.DateTime.Kind%2A> 의 속성을 `time` 개체 <xref:System.DateTimeKind.Local?displayProperty=nameWithType>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0879c-230">If you want to specify the time in local time, then specify the <xref:System.DateTime.Kind%2A> property of the `time` object as <xref:System.DateTimeKind.Local?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="0879c-231">다음 코드는 ADAM 인스턴스 포트 번호 "5000."에서 "adamHost1.fabrikam.com" 서버에서 호스트에 연결</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0879c-231">The following code connects to the ADAM instance hosted by the server "adamHost1.fabrikam.com" on port number "5000."</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0879c-232">(AdamAdmin), username 및 password (SecretPwd123)에 지정 된 된 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> 생성자입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0879c-232">The username (adamAdmin), and password (SecretPwd123) are specified in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0879c-233">컨테이너 아래 모든 인증 가능 보안 주체에 대 한 검색을 수행 하는 "DC adamApp1, DC = fabrikam, DC = com ="는 로그인 되지이 ADAM 인스턴스 지난 45 일간 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0879c-233">A search is performed for all authenticable principals under the container "DC=adamApp1,DC=fabrikam,DC=com" that have not logged on to this ADAM instance for the last 45 days.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0879c-234">검색에서 반환 된 보안 주체 삭제 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0879c-234">The principals returned by the search are then deleted.</span></span>  
  
```  
PrincipalContext ctx = new PrincipalContext(  
                                      ContextType.ApplicationDirectory,   
                                      "adamHost1.fabrikam.com:5000",   
                                      "DC=adamApp1,DC=fabrikam,DC=com",   
                                      "adamAdmin", "SecretPwd123");  
  
PrincipalSearchResult<AuthenticablePrincipal> oldPrincipals =   
                     AuthenticablePrincipal.FindByLogonTime(ctx,   
                            (DateTime.Now - new TimeSpan(45, 0, 0, 0)),   
                            MatchType.LessThan);  
  
foreach (Principal p in oldPrincipals)  
{  
    p.Delete();  
}  
  
oldPrincipals.Dispose();  
ctx.Dispose();  
  
```

